  "description": [
    "Pick Handle Fred Lost Ray Conies To The SCENERY O In the Democratic section of Meet Your Candidates pub lished by the Welch Daily News under date of October 17th Mr Fred L Ray Candidate for Sheriff on the Democratic Paaty has his picture emblazoned upon the second page dedicated to the Democratic Candidates and with a flow of words beyond our comprehension he seeks to inform the electorate of McDowell County just why he should be elected sheriff Perhaps we are just plain dumb unimaginative folks failing as we have to keep up with the trend of the times as laid down to us by the New Deal Regulations We hope Mr Ray can pardon us for that inasmuch as we have had more important things to en gage our attention We must confess that we were rather beguiled by your poli tical advertisement because the party of the opposition has charged you with certain things that would indicate a character very much in variance with that claimed in this particular politi cal advertisement In order to set us straight as to the truth or falsity of such a dual personality as the claims of yourself and your opposition"
  ],
